previous.message: The first time I stole so that I wouldn’t starve, yes. I lost many assumptions about the simple nature of right and wrong. And when I traveled, I learned the fear before a crime and the thrill of success. But I never became one of them.
previous.author: batman

current.message: To conquer fear, you must become fear.
current.author: batman

next.message: You always fear what you don’t understand.
next.author: batman
